.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
\fB--unpackaged-only\fR
.ad
.sp .6
.RS 4n
Report only unpackaged contents. This option excludes general verification
output and only reports the unpackaged files and directories. This option can
be combined with \fB--parsable\fR
.RE

