Parsable output; the supported version is 0. Use of this option implies
\fB-q\fR.
.RE

.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
\fB--unpackaged\fR
.ad
.sp .6
.RS 4n
Report unpackaged contents in addition to general output.
.RE

For all other options, see the \fBinstall\fR command above.
