.ne 2
.mk
.na
\fB\fB--tagged\fR \fItag-name\fR\fR
.ad
.sp .6
.RS 4n
Revert all files tagged with \fItag-name\fR, and remove any unpackaged files or directories that are under directories with this tag and that match \fIpattern\fR. See the description of the \fBrevert-tag\fR attribute in "File Actions" and "Directory Actions" in the \fBpkg\fR(7) man page for more information about \fBtag-name\fR and \fIpattern\fR.
.RE

